Global Music Streaming Software and Platforms Market Insights
Music Streaming Software and Platforms Market size was valued at USD 22.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 39.4 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.8% from 2024 to 2030.

Music Streaming Software and Platforms Market Overview
The global music streaming software and platforms market was valued at approximately USD 27.87 billion in 2023 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 17.3% from 2023 to 2030, reaching an estimated market value of USD 102.52 billion by 2030. This growth is fueled by increasing internet penetration, the rise of mobile devices, and growing consumer demand for on-demand music streaming. As music consumption shifts from traditional media to digital, the market continues to attract investment from leading tech giants like Spotify, Apple Music, and Amazon Music.

